import React from 'react' import './checkout.styles.scss' import {connect} from 'react-redux' import {createStructuredSelector} from 'reselect' import{selectCartItems,selectCartTotal} from '../../redux/cart/cart.selectors' const CheckOutPage =()=>(
Product
Description
Quantity
Price
Remove
) mapStateToProps = createStructuredSelector({ cartItems:selectCartItems, total: selectCartTotal }) export default connect(mapStateToProps)(CheckOutPage)
